      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PATH TO NIRVANA (8) doesn't win out of turn. Finished in the money last time though when second (16.92) at this track. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from five attempts. Can measure up this time. ASTON TRANSCEND (1) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 19.68 beating Darra Mick. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Can make it back-to-back wins. CINDY CABANG (6) missed the frame two back but wound up strongly last time, finishing on late when third (22.88) in a Grade 5 at Geelong. Form at the trip sound including six wins. Won at her only start from this box. Will give a great sight again. MOTIVATE (2) will need to run right up to last start to feature again.",
